<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】AgenticSTS项目用五个独立的记忆层替代了AI智能体不断增长的聊天记录。在卡牌游戏《杀戮尖塔2》中测试时，提示词保持在约5000个token，而非膨胀至50万个以上。该智能体在10局游戏中获胜6局，而竞争智能体则一局未胜。本文《AI agents win at Slay the Spire 2 after researchers replace growing chat logs with structured memory》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/ai-agents-win-at-slay-the-spire-2-after-researchers-replace-growing-chat-logs-with-structured-memory/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
