<title>OpenAI的GPT-5.6 Sol Ultra据称在一小时内解决了一个50年未解的数学难题</title>
<link>https://the-decoder.com/openais-gpt-5-6-sol-ultra-reportedly-solves-a-50-year-old-math-problem-in-under-an-hour/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=37656</guid>
<pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2026 17:38:35 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】OpenAI的GPT-5.6 Sol Ultra在不到一小时内，通过64个子代理并行工作，给出了“循环双覆盖猜想”的证明。该猜想已悬而未决50年。数学家托马斯·布鲁姆称该证明出人意料地基础，但批评其缺乏对已知先前工作的引用。更大的问题依然存在：AI只是重新组合现有知识，还是创造了新东西？文章《OpenAI's GPT-5.6 Sol Ultra reportedly solves a 50-year-old math problem in under an hour》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/openais-gpt-5-6-sol-ultra-reportedly-solves-a-50-year-old-math-problem-in-under-an-hour/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
</item>
